<title><%= title %></title>
<div class="relative flex-grow flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden fade-in min-h-[80dvh]">
    <!-- Background Accents -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full pointer-events-none -z-10">
        <div class="absolute top-[-5%] left-[-10%] w-[60%] h-[60%] bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] mix-blend-multiply opacity-70"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-accent/15 rounded-full blur-[100px] mix-blend-multiply opacity-70"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 md:py-20 text-center">
        <!-- Logo Branding -->
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-8 md:mb-10">
            <div class="relative group">
                <div class="absolute -inset-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent rounded-[2.5rem] blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-60 transition duration-700"></div>
                <img src="/favicon.jpg" alt="PuZero Logo" class="relative w-24 h-24 sm:w-28 sm:h-28 md:w-32 md:h-32 rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl border-4 border-white object-cover">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-slate-200/60 text-slate-600 text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold mb-8 shadow-sm">
            <span class="relative flex h-2.5 w-2.5">
                <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-75"></span>
                <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2.5 w-2.5 bg-primary"></span>
            </span>
            All-in-One AI Productivity Hub
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-secondary tracking-tight mb-6 md:mb-8 leading-[1.15] md:leading-[1.1]">
            Optimalkan Pekerjaan <br class="hidden sm:block">
            Dengan <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent">PuZero AI.</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 mb-10 md:mb-12 leading-relaxed font-medium px-2">
            Platform serba guna yang dirancang untuk membantu Anda mengunduh media, mengolah data, dan meningkatkan produktivitas menggunakan teknologi AI terbaru.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 w-full max-w-md mx-auto sm:max-w-none">
            <a hx-get="/category" hx-target="#main-content" hx-push-url="true" class="w-full sm:w-auto cursor-pointer px-8 py-4 sm:py-5 bg-secondary text-white rounded-2xl font-black text-base sm:text-lg hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 active:scale-95 group">
                Mulai Sekarang
                <i class="ph-bold ph-arrow-right group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
            </a>
            <a hx-get="/features" hx-target="#main-content" hx-push-url="true" class="w-full sm:w-auto cursor-pointer px-8 py-4 sm:py-5 bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 text-slate-600 rounded-2xl font-bold text-base sm:text-lg hover:border-primary/30 hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-primary transition-all active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center">
                Pelajari Fitur
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-20 md:mt-28 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-lightning text-2xl md:text-3xl text-amber-500"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Fast Speed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-shield-check text-2xl md:text-3xl text-emerald-500"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Secure</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-infinity text-2xl md:text-3xl text-blue-500"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Unlimited</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-currency-circle-dollar text-2xl md:text-3xl text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[10px] md:text-xs text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-widest">100% Free</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
